pr_title: Room based implementation of Local track database layer
pr_body:
# Description
Newly created track database layer based on android Room.

Fixes #532  

## Task
- [x] Local track database layer implementation based on Sqlite database with Room.
- [x] First test on real device.
- [x] Unit testing Room DAO classes.
